<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TT2.3">
<l>puṭkaḷ potutta pulālveṇ ṭalaiyaip puṟamē narikavva</l>
<l>vaṭkeṉ ṟaḻaippa vāntai vīca varukē ciṟukūkai</l>
<l>yuṭka viḻikka vūmaṉ veruṭṭa vōri katitteṅkum</l>
<l>piṭka naṭṭam pēṇu miṟaivaṉ peyarum peruṅkāṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>While outside jackals seize stinking white skulls that had been pecked by birds,</l>
<l>wherever, while, in order to shreak harshly, owlets flap [their] wings,</l>
<l>so that the littel owls nearby are in terror, hyenas howl to frighten owls,</l>
<l>noisily the lord who cherishes dancing moves in the great cremation ground.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
